# Local scratch / Claude Code state
.claude/
# ...but each shipped version carries its Claude Code config (slash command, subagents, settings).
# Plant ships three coding-agent variants, so its config lives under Claude/; Medical and Animal
# are Claude-only, so their .claude sits at the version root.
!Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/
!Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/agents/
!Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/agents/**
!Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/commands/
!Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/commands/**
!Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/settings.json
!Flash-P_Medical/.claude/
!Flash-P_Medical/.claude/agents/
!Flash-P_Medical/.claude/agents/**
!Flash-P_Medical/.claude/commands/
!Flash-P_Medical/.claude/commands/**
!Flash-P_Medical/.claude/settings.json
!Flash-P_Animal/.claude/
!Flash-P_Animal/.claude/agents/
!Flash-P_Animal/.claude/agents/**
!Flash-P_Animal/.claude/commands/
!Flash-P_Animal/.claude/commands/**
!Flash-P_Animal/.claude/settings.json
# ...but never the personal/runtime state inside them
Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/settings.local.json
Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/*.lock
Flash-P_Plant/Claude/.claude/worktrees/
Flash-P_Medical/.claude/settings.local.json
Flash-P_Medical/.claude/*.lock
Flash-P_Medical/.claude/worktrees/
Flash-P_Animal/.claude/settings.local.json
Flash-P_Animal/.claude/*.lock
Flash-P_Animal/.claude/worktrees/
*.log
*.tmp

